Description:
Amazing Quality Just Metres From The Best School in Cranbourne East!
Set in a brilliant location in the ever popular Hunt Club Estate within Cranbourne East, situated on a 544m2 block, this gorgeous ultra-modern 4 bedroom home simply oozes class and sophisticated living with its modern appearance throughout.
Upon entry, you'll be greeted will an elegant entrance and beautiful polished tiled floor throughout. This home offers a spacious lounge room, stunning open plan kitchen fully equipped with stainless steel appliances, ample cupboard and bench space including the huge island bench which adjourns the homely meals area. Four large bedrooms, master with walk in robe, huge full ensuite with separate toilet, oversized shower and spacious his and her vanity. Remaining 2, 3 & 4 bedrooms are complete with built in robes and serviced by the central and well-appointed bathroom which includes a bath, shower, and single vanity. Adding to this extremely desirable property is a bonus feature of a home theatre room/second living area, which is perfect for entertaining the whole family.
Outside you'll be impressed by the alfresco, which overlooks the private and manicured low maintenance rear garden with the additional extra of a small garden shed for extra storage. Double Garage is also featured with both internal and external access.
Additional Luxuries include;
* An array of quality pendant lights and down lights throughout
* Ducted heating
* Split system heating/cooling unit
* Landscaping to the front and rear yard
Within close proximity to all that Cranbourne East has to offer including: Public transport, an abundance of schooling, sporting/recreational facilities, Cranbourne Racecourse and Cranbourne Park Shopping Centre, this home is truly a winner and will definitely leave you feeling spoilt.

Description:
UNDER CONTRACT/ UNDER OFFER!
CRANBOURNE EAST: Attention all first home buyers, investors and downsizers you couldnt ask for better opportunity than 13 Willowbank Drive! Within a short distance to all amenities this one certainly ticks all of the boxes!
This property features a functional floorplan consisting of 3 bedrooms, master complete with ensuite and WIR. Both of the 2nd & 3rd bedrooms are a good size and are central to the family bathroom with separate toilet. Multiple living areas consisting of a front formal lounge, Separate dining area/ open study depending on what you would like to use it for and the kitchen/meals area. The kitchen has plenty of bench and cupboard space, gas cooktop and oven.
Internal extras include gas ducted heating, split system air con, mix of tiles and carpet and neutral paint tones throughout.
Outside you will find a single garage with rear access through to the huge pergola that could be easy doubled up as a carport, a care free backyard allowing you to add your own personal touches as you see fit with the option to potentially add some gates to the side fencing and have side access as well making this perfect for caravans, boats and extra cars.
Surrounded by established homes the property itself is only moments from all of the amenities on offer in the Hunt Club together with childcare and medical facilities, local primary/high schools and Chisholm Tafe! Not to forget the recently opened shopping development on Linsell Boulevard, only a short walk away, offering Safeway, Aldi, takeaway and shopping outlets!
BOOK AN INSPECTION TODAY, IT MAY BE GONE TOMORROW! - *PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT OPEN FOR INSPECTIONS*!
The Hunt Club is a multi award winning estate offering numerous parks, wetlands, walking and bicycle paths as well as a complete range of childcare, primary (Cranbourne East Primary) and secondary schools (Cranbourne East Secondary College). Buses weave through the estate making the newly built shopping centre complete with Woolworths & Aldi easily accessible. Recycled water, high speed broadband and environmentally friendly designs are all part of the estate.

Description:
SOLD BY MATTHEW RINGERI!
CRANBOURNE EAST: If you are looking to buy a house where you can simply move in, unpack and relax then 21 Dash Drive needs to be seen to be appreciated!
Constructed by well known builders Fairhaven Homes Special Projects this complete package measures some 35 squares of living and is nestled on a massive app. 792m2 block!
With a functional, free flowing floor plan the property itself features 4 generous bedrooms plus an open study. The master offers a WIR and a FES providing double shower with dumper, dual vanities and massive deep bath to enjoy at the end of a hard day. Bedrooms 2, 3 and 4, all with walk in robes, are in close proximity to the family bathroom with separate bath and shower facilities.
The hostess kitchen is the central hub of the home and is finished with huge amounts of cupboard space, bench tops, glass splash back, quality appliances including 900mm free standing oven with 5-burner hot plate, 900mm rangehood with glass canopy plus stainless steel dishwasher, island bench and wide fridge cavity. The butlers pantry completes this already fantastic kitchen. Fitted out with the same quality it offers plenty more cupboard and bench space, sink, extra oven and built in microwave with direct access to the great sized laundry. All this overlooking the tiled family meals zone with sliding door access to the underroof alfresco!
Take advantage of the 4 separate living zones making year round formal and informal entertaining a breeze! Relax with a good book and a quiet glass of your finest wine in the front sitting area, carefree day to day living will be enjoyed in tiled family zone, rear rumpus/theatre room for the kids or hang out in the pool room with your very own built in bar with sink, fridge cavity, wine wrack and plenty of bench and cupboard space.
Added internal extras include downlights, ducted heating, powder room, quality floor coverings and neutral colour tones throughout
Step outside and be greeted by a sensational street scape offering a modern facade and picturesque landscaping. A lengthy concrete driveway leads to the over sized remote garage which has room for 2 cars and a workshop. There is internal access plus an side access to the side of the house. For all those with extra cars, boats, caravans, work equipment the 2nd driveway with crossover and side gates for access to the rear yard surely must be a huge bonus.
The Hunt Club is a multi award winning estate offering numerous parks, wetlands, walking and bicycle paths as well as a complete range of childcare, primary (Cranbourne East Primary) and secondary schools (Cranbourne East Secondary College). Buses weave through the estate making the newly built shopping centre complete with Woolworths & Aldi easily accessible. Recycled water, high speed broadband and environmentally friendly designs are all part of the estate.

Description:
Perfect position in the Hunt Club
CRANBOURNE EAST - (HUNT CLUB) - Sitting on approx. 563sqm is this beautiful home, consisting of 3 large bedrooms plus study/fourth bedroom, master with full ensuite and WIR.
The property has a natural flow in the layout which offers a fantastic formal lounge flowing into a large open plan family living area and dining area. All of this is overlooked by a large spacious kitchen with stainless steel appliances as well as plenty of cupboard and bench space to complete the picture.
On offer there is also a massive undercover outdoor area which is perfect for entertaining family and friends all year round, as well as a fantastic landscaped backyard for the kids to play.
Other extras in the property include, ducted heating & split system cooling, fully landscaped gardens back and front, nine foot celling's, fantastic plaster work and much more.
The property is located within a very short walking distance to the Cranbourne East primary & secondary schools, the child care centre, parks, wetlands and public transport.
All the hard work has been done for you which makes this property a perfect place for a large family to grow.

SOLD BY ZED!
Imagine being able to call the removalists and simply unpack, move in and relax with nothing else to do! At 3 Foxhound Grove, all your dreams will come true.
As you walk through this amazing property, you are greeted with high ceilings and downlights throughout, a study to your left that at your convenience can be used as a sixth bedroom, a formal lounge and an open plan living area which offers plenty of space, the kitchen features a 900ml oven, stainless steel appliances, a glass splash back and stone bench tops means the chef of the family will fall in-love.
In total there are five good sized bedrooms all with spotted gum floorboards, the master bedroom features walk in robe and an en-suite with double vanity meaning no fights in the morning, outdoor features a pergola area as well as a decent sized backyard for you to enjoy entertaining friends or even have a kick of the footy with your kids.
Other features include - ducted heating, split system, quality light fixtures, alarm system, landscaped front and rear yard and a colourbond fence surrounding the property, giving you the extra privacy you need as well as a double garage that has the added bonus of a second kitchen with lots of cupboard space.
Located in a superb location, within walking distance to Cranbourne East P-12 school and Early learning centre & child care centre, short drive to Cranbourne East shopping centre (Woolworths & Aldi), Selandra Rise shopping centre and the newly renovated Cranbourne Park Shopping Centre as well as being in close proximity to Casey Grammer School, Casey Race Leisure Centre and the Cranbourne Library â?? this is one not to be missed, call today before it is too late.
